name: Vitamin - Extras kit
description:
​​Decathlon's Extras Kit includes useful components that you can use for prototypes and designs.

 

Full documentation: Decathlon.design

 

In this library, you will find:

  • Web cursors
  • Web navigation bars
  • Android & iOS native keyboards
  • Dark & Light mode 
  • Emoji keyboard
  • Dictation mode
  • Numeric keyboard

 

Read the CHANGELOG.


Suggestion and/or feedback are welcome. Feel free to contact us thanks to this feedback form.
